            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "d1e52e9ca86f_11",
          "href": null,
          "name": "600d",
          "text": "The Whole Systems Design Framework underlying the EDE (Face-to-Face) and GEDS (online) programmes of Gaia Education",
