          "href": null,
          "name": "02ed",
          "text": "Daniel Christian Wahl has been a member of Gaia Education since 2007 and co-directed the Findhorn Foundation College between 2007 and 2010. Daniel in 2012 presenting at Gaia Home, Cupola dos Povos during Rio+20. (image)",
