          "text": "Daniel Wahl has worked with Gaia Education since 2007 and is a co-author of all four dimensions of the GEDS curriculum. Many of the meta-design changes of scale-linking, salutogenic design for whole systems health which he explored in depth in his PhD on Design for Human and Planetary Health (2006) are woven throughout Gaia Education’s online programme in Design for Sustainability.",
